236
00:09:07,999 --> 00:09:09,000
That's great.

237
00:09:09,041 --> 00:09:10,251
When can you move in?

238
00:09:10,293 --> 00:09:12,837
Uh, duh. Now.

239
00:09:12,878 --> 00:09:14,714
<i>And with his living</i>
<i>arrangements taken care of,</i>

240
00:09:14,755 --> 00:09:16,966
