<i>court-appointed work-release.</i>

241
00:09:17,008 --> 00:09:18,510
One, two, three, four, five...

242
00:09:18,551 --> 00:09:21,304
<i>And so began</i>
<i>an intense workshop to create</i>

243
00:09:21,346 --> 00:09:25,099
<i>the</i>Fantastic Four<i>musical,</i>
