244
00:09:25,141 --> 00:09:27,393
Now, the script is in process,
but the goal is

245
00:09:27,435 --> 00:09:30,104
that we all get a little outing
on the Cinco de Cuatro,

246
00:09:30,146 --> 00:09:32,440
where we'll be performing it
on a boat.

247
00:09:32,482 --> 00:09:34,192
I hope no one gets seasick.

248
00:09:34,233 --> 00:09:38,070
Okay. And Mark Cherry is going
to be doing the music for us.

