00:09:57,256 --> 00:09:59,551
Out, back, step, shuffle...

261
00:09:59,592 --> 00:10:01,344
<i>And even though</i>
<i>DeBrie had some trouble</i>

262
00:10:01,386 --> 00:10:03,680
<i>with the choreography</i>
<i>at first...</i>

263
00:10:03,722 --> 00:10:05,139
