- DeBrie! -DeBrie!

264
00:10:05,181 --> 00:10:06,516
- Oh, God.
- Are you all right?

265
00:10:06,558 --> 00:10:07,808
- Yeah, yeah.
- Baby steps, Argyle.

266
00:10:07,850 --> 00:10:09,227
She's brittle.

267
00:10:09,268 --> 00:10:11,312
Tobias, it does not
get babier than this.

268
00:10:11,354 --> 00:10:13,189
- Maybe I can't do this.
- You can do it.

269
00:10:13,231 --> 00:10:15,107
Tobias, I can do it.
I used to be a hoofer.

270
00:10:15,149 --> 00:10:16,984
(chuckles)
Well, now you're a huffer...

271
00:10:17,026 --> 00:10:19,820
<i>If dancing wasn't her strength,</i>
<i>Tobias had no doubt</i>

