00:10:19,862 --> 00:10:22,490
<i>she'd wow them</i>
<i>with her showstopping solo.</i>

273
00:10:22,532 --> 00:10:24,867
♪ I don't want to be invisible ♪

274
00:10:24,909 --> 00:10:29,622
♪ I don't want to be
invisible anymore... ♪

275
00:10:29,664 --> 00:10:30,956
(laughs):
Okay, good.

276
00:10:30,998 --> 00:10:31,957
Well, get out there.

277
00:10:31,999 --> 00:10:33,042
All right.

278
00:10:33,084 --> 00:10:34,919
Okay-- oh, I like this, too.

279
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,962
I-- oh, where's Argyle?
She's choreographing.

280
00:10:37,004 --> 00:10:39,006
Let's all do it, too.

281
00:10:39,048 --> 00:10:40,592
And we'll just follow her lead.

282
00:10:40,633 --> 00:10:43,094
When she comes up,
we come up as a group.

283
00:10:44,053 --> 00:10:45,930
So, DeBrie, when you come up,

284
00:10:45,971 --> 00:10:48,391
- we shall rise with you.
- (DeBrie groaning loudly)

285
00:10:48,433 --> 00:10:50,393
(others groaning loudly)

286
00:10:50,435 --> 00:10:52,311
Go with her! Go!

287
00:10:52,353 --> 00:10:53,479
Follow her! Follow her!

288
00:10:53,521 --> 00:10:54,689
Go!

289
00:10:54,731 --> 00:10:58,610
Am I crazy,
or is this really good?

290
00:10:58,651 --> 00:11:02,154
♪ I'm gonna stomp
all over your face ♪

291
00:11:02,196 --> 00:11:05,784
♪ Even if my heart
