- Good night.

410
00:15:00,225 --> 00:15:01,226
George Michael, hey.

411
00:15:01,268 --> 00:15:02,520
Got out of it.

412
00:15:02,561 --> 00:15:04,814
I just-- I made
a ton of people angry,

413
00:15:04,856 --> 00:15:06,816
but you know what I always say:
family...

414
00:15:06,858 --> 00:15:09,027
GEORGE MICHAEL: Well, ah, gosh,
you know, I really wanted to,

415
00:15:09,068 --> 00:15:12,279
uh, do that, but I just had
this work thing come up.

416
00:15:12,321 --> 00:15:14,073
And, uh, it's like
you always say:

417
00:15:14,114 --> 00:15:16,701
family first,
unless there's a work thing,

418
00:15:16,742 --> 00:15:18,160
and then work first.

419
00:15:18,202 --> 00:15:19,745
I have said that, too.

420
00:15:19,787 --> 00:15:23,123
Well, I've got politics
and producing stuff I can...

421
00:15:23,165 --> 00:15:25,459
<i>After being kicked out</i>
<i>of his son's dorm</i>

422
00:15:25,501 --> 00:15:27,252
<i>and stood up</i>
<i>at the Ealing Club,</i>

423
00:15:27,294 --> 00:15:29,505
<i>this particular rejection</i>
<i>really hurt.</i>

424
00:15:29,547 --> 00:15:30,882
Another time.

425
00:15:30,923 --> 00:15:32,717
<i>But he tried to put on</i>
<i>a brave face</i>

426
00:15:32,758 --> 00:15:34,927
<i>when he ran into a woman</i>
<i>he was in debt to.</i>

427
00:15:34,969 --> 00:15:37,013
- Who is this?
- Oh, this is

428
00:15:37,055 --> 00:15:38,180
my baby brother, Argyle.

429
00:15:38,222 --> 00:15:39,849
And here's the family joke:

430
00:15:39,891 --> 00:15:42,685
I'm a tall drink of water,
and he's the chaser.

431
00:15:42,727 --> 00:15:43,686
(both laugh)

432
00:15:43,728 --> 00:15:46,022
Should be flipped, right?

433
00:15:46,064 --> 00:15:48,900
No, because here's another joke:
you owe my sister

434
00:15:48,941 --> 00:15:52,904
$700,000, and I'm going to
chase you down until you pay up.

435
00:15:52,945 --> 00:15:54,947
And if you don't pay up
by the fourth,

436
00:15:54,989 --> 00:15:56,407
you're gonna be washing up

437
00:15:56,448 --> 00:15:58,910
with the rest of
the broken piñatas on the fifth.

438
00:15:58,951 --> 00:16:00,327
WOMAN:
Lucille!

439
00:16:00,369 --> 00:16:01,328
Oh, hello.

440
00:16:01,370 --> 00:16:02,663
Who's-- ow, ow!

441
00:16:02,705 --> 00:16:04,164
God, what is on the bottom
of those shoes?

442
00:16:04,206 --> 00:16:05,541
Taps.

443
00:16:05,583 --> 00:16:08,210
And I can tap dance
all over your face,

444
00:16:08,252 --> 00:16:09,628
if you know what I mean.

445
00:16:09,670 --> 00:16:10,922
Even if my heart won't

446
00:16:10,963 --> 00:16:12,631
