- (snaps fingers)

447
00:16:12,673 --> 00:16:14,550
I don't know what you meant
with the last part there.

448
00:16:14,592 --> 00:16:17,053
I'll chase you down
and find you, Michael.

449
00:16:17,095 --> 00:16:19,179
You can't hide
in a gorilla suit from me.

450
00:16:19,221 --> 00:16:22,474
(tapping shoes rhythmically)

451
00:16:22,516 --> 00:16:23,976
♪<i>Mr. F.</i>♪

452
00:16:24,018 --> 00:16:25,477
<i>Argyle was wrong on that count.</i>

453
00:16:25,519 --> 00:16:28,898
<i>It was Buster</i>
<i>who wore the gorilla suit.</i>

454
00:16:28,940 --> 00:16:31,233
ARGYLE: <i>He's a producer,</i>
<i>and he says he'll pay up.</i>

455
00:16:31,275 --> 00:16:32,860
Any progress on the rights?

456
00:16:32,902 --> 00:16:34,653
I'm in talks with Imagine.

457
00:16:34,695 --> 00:16:35,780
