- (dial tone)

463
00:16:43,495 --> 00:16:46,124
Well, then you're gonna have
to work with our new patient,

464
00:16:46,165 --> 00:16:47,416
and good luck with her.

465
00:16:47,458 --> 00:16:49,627
We call her the "B" word
from the "C" ward.

466
00:16:49,668 --> 00:16:51,963
Or is it the "C" word
from the "B" ward?

467
00:16:52,004 --> 00:16:53,756
(knocks)

